Third-party components and licensing
======================================

Ableton Link (optional native dependency)
-----------------------------------------
To build `link_shim.dll`, you clone [Ableton/link](https://github.com/Ableton/link)
into `native/third_party/link`. Ableton Link and the `native/link-shim` wrapper are
under **GNU GPL version 2 or later (GPL-2.0+)**. Building or redistributing
binaries that include `link_shim.dll` must comply with that license (including
source-offer requirements where applicable).

Link’s build may pull **Asio** via Git submodule; see the Link repository for
Asio’s license terms.

Official release policy (this repository)
-----------------------------------------
Published release artifacts from this project are intended **not** to ship
`link_shim.dll`. End users who want Ableton Link BPM mode build the shim locally;
see `docs/agents/native-link-shim-build.md`.
